tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE parking_data (
  parking_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  parking_location VARCHAR(255),
  parking_status VARCHAR(50),
  car_plate_number VARCHAR(20),
  check_in_time TIMESTAMP,
  check_out_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE parking_lots (
  parking_lot_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  parking_lot_name TEXT,
  total_spaces INT,
  available_spaces INT
)

CREATE TABLE parking_log (
  log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  parking_lot_id UUID,
  entry_time TIMESTAMP,
  exit_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE parking_history (
  entry_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  spot_id INT,
  entry_time TIMESTAMP,
  exit_time TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (spot_id) REFERENCES parking_spots(spot_id)
);

CREATE TABLE parking_lots (
  lot_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  lot_name VARCHAR(50),
  location VARCHAR(100),
  total_spaces INT,
  available_spaces INT
)

CREATE TABLE parking_sensors (
  sensor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  lot_id INT,
  floor INT,
  sensor_type VARCHAR(20),
  status VARCHAR(10)
)

CREATE TABLE parking_transactions (
  transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  sensor_id INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  vehicle_plate VARCHAR(15),
  payment_amount DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE parking_statistics (
  stat_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  lot_id INT,
  date DATE,
  total_visits INT,
  revenue DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE parking_lots (
    lot_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    capacity INT,
    current_occupancy INT,
    status VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE vehicles (
    vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    license_plate VARCHAR(50),
    vehicle_type VARCHAR(50),
    user_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(user_id)
)

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(100),
    email VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE parking_events (
    event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    lot_id INT,
    enter_time TIMESTAMP,
    exit_time TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (vehicle_id) REFERENCES vehicles(vehicle_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (lot_id) REFERENCES parking_lots(lot_id)
)

CREATE TABLE payments (
    payment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    event_id INT,
    amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    payment_time TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (event_id) REFERENCES parking_events(event_id)
)
